headline: This Top Warren Buffett Stock Continues to Get Better as It Grows Bigger
summary: Warren Buffett's company, Berkshire Hathaway (NYSE: BRK.A)(NYSE: BRK.B), has invested nearly $290 billion into a portfolio of publicly traded companies.  Berkshire owns 118.6 million shares worth $19.8 billion, which is 6.9% of its investment portfolio.  There are lots of oil stocks Buffett's company could have bought.
